    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1620557/" class="title-link">08年最大的读书收获之一</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1620557"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3502242/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3502242-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3502242/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">山巅白云</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-01-15"
      class="main-meta">2009-01-15 18:16:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1620557_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  与钱穆的《中国历代政治得失》、吴思的《隐蔽的秩序——历史的弈局》互相参照，对中国历史会有更多的理解。 这是今年感觉收获比较多的书，是实实在在的收获，不只是增加历史知识。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
